      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- \"have to'\n    - if you want to create \"cloud native\" apps\n    you have to do these things -\n        - port binding\n\n - other things are \"this is the antidote to ways we did\nthings in the past that proved to be less than ideal\"\n\n\n- Dependencies -\n    Code we didn't write, we don't maintain but\nwe make a lot of money off of.\n    - These could be early bound (NuGet Packages)\n        - early bound are compiled with and delivered with our app.\n    - Late bound \n       - these are \"resolved' at run time - probably the biggest source\n          of production issues.\n       - examples -\n           databases\n           identity\n           other APIS\n            (12FA calls these \"backing services\" and \"attached resources\")\n\n    \ndon't do things like have a \"libs\" folder full of dlls in your source control.\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- \"have to'\n    - if you want to create \"cloud native\" apps\n    you have to do these things -\n        - port binding\n\n - other things are \"this is the antidote to ways we did\nthings in the past that proved to be less than ideal\"\n\n\n- Dependencies -\n    Code we didn't write, we don't maintain but\nwe make a lot of money off of.\n    - These could be early bound (NuGet Packages)\n        - early bound are compiled with and delivered with our app.\n    - Late bound \n       - these are \"resolved' at run time - probably the biggest source\n          of production issues.\n       - examples -\n           databases\n           identity\n           other APIS\n            (12FA calls these \"backing services\" and \"attached resources\")\n\n    \ndon't do things like have a \"libs\" folder full of dlls in your source control.\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
