      "locked": false,
      "text": "late bound - databases, idp, other apis\n    - these will change based on environment.\n    - that makes them \"config\"\n\n- There is no such thing as a distributed transaction.\n    - Just a fact.\n    - All of our architecture for DECADES has been based on transactional consistency.\n\n- eventual consistency\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "late bound - databases, idp, other apis\n    - these will change based on environment.\n    - that makes them \"config\"\n\n- There is no such thing as a distributed transaction.\n    - Just a fact.\n    - All of our architecture for DECADES has been based on transactional consistency.\n\n- eventual consistency\n",
